<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Car Rental</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/bstyle.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/boxicons@latest/css/boxicons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-zCbKRCUGaJDkqS1kPbPd7TveP5iyJE0EjAuZQTgFLD2ylzuqKfdKlfG/eSrtxUkn" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.2.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-KJ3o2DKtIkvYIK3UENzmM7KCkRr/rE9/Qpg6aAZGJwFDMVNA/GpGFF93hXpG5KkN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.0.0/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-JZR6Spejh4U02d8jOt6vLEHfe/JQGiRRSQQxSfFWpi1MquVdAyjUar5+76PVCmYl" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.12.9/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-ApNbgh9B+Y1QKtv3Rn7W3mgPxhU9K/ScQsAP7hUibX39j7fakFPskvXusvfa0b4Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
    <style>
        .card{
           border-bottom-width: 15px;
         }
         .rent-btn{
             margin-top: 20px;
             border-color: yellow;
         }
         .username{
             color: yellow;
             border-color: yellow;
         }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark">            
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="#" ><img src="./img/logo.png" alt="top-logo"></a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbarNav" aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
              <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
          
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav p-4 col-sm">
                    <li><a style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;" href="#home">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;" href="#ride">Ride</a></li>
                    <li><a style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;" href="#services">Services</a></li>
                    <li><a style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;" href="#about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;" href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
                    <% if(publish){ %>
                        <li><a style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;" href="/publish-ride">Publish a ride</a></li>
                    <% } %>
                </ul>
                
                <% if(!user){ %>
                <div class="header-btn">
                    <a href="/register" class="sign-up">Sign Up</a>
                    <a href="/login" class="sign-in">Sign In</a>
                </div>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/">
                        <button type="button" class="username btn btn-outline-secondary" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" data-bs-placement="top"
                            data-bs-custom-class="custom-tooltip" title="Click to log out.">
                                <%= userName %> 
                        </button>
                    </a>
                <% } %>
                
            </div>    
        </nav>
    </header>

   
    <!-- Home -->
    <section class="home" id="home">
        <div class="text">
            <h1><span> Hey! <br> Wanna Have <br> A Ride, <br></span> We Got You Covered...</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="taxi">
            <img src="/img/taxi.png" alt="taxi-img">
        </div>

        <% if(!user){ %>
            <a href="/register">
            <button class="rent-btn btn btn-outline-primary" style="color:rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration: none;">Rent Now</button>
            </a>
        <% } %>

        <% if(user) {%>
            <%- include('search'); -%>
        <% } %>

    </section>

    <!-- Ride -->
    <section class="ride" id="ride">
        <div class="heading">
            <span>How Its Work</span>
            <h1>Rent With 3 Easy Steps</h1>
        </div>

    <div class="ride-container">

        <div class="card-deck">

                <div class="card" style="background-color: yellow;">
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="card-header">
                            <i class='bx bxs-map'></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2>Choose A Location</h2>
                            <p>Picks up Location from over 273 busy streets from rural to urban, you name it and there
                                is no stopping anytime soon.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
    
                <div class="card" style="background-color: yellow;">
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="card-header">
                            <i class='bx bxs-calendar-check'></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2>Pick-Up Date</h2>
                            <p>A date, Um-Oh, Just Scroll Your Calendar and lock it up as we are there 7-days a week
                                anytime.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card" style="background-color: yellow;">
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="card-header">
                            <i class='bx bxs-calendar-star'></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h2>Book A Car</h2>
                            <p>We offer you more than 30-Models of Cars to choose from, Just look and decide what suits
                                you or makes you happy.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

    <!-- Services -->
            <section class="services" id="services">
                <div class="heading">
                    <span>Best Services</span>
                    <h1>Share your any rides with Carpool</h1>
                </div>
                <div class="services-container">
                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="box-img">
                            <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/1056x594/n/cw/ec/41564/hyundai-creta-right-front-three-quarter9.jpeg?q=75&wm=1"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Hyundai Creta</h3>
                        <h2>Rs.20<span>/KM</span></h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="box-img">
                            <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/1056x594/n/cw/ec/54399/exterior-right-front-three-quarter-10.jpeg?q=75&wm=1"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Maruti Suzuki Swift</h3>
                        <h2>Rs.15 <span>/KM</span></h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="box-img">
                            <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/1056x594/n/cw/ec/41645/tata-nexon-right-front-three-quarter3.jpeg?q=75&wm=1"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Tata Nexon</h3>
                        <h2>Rs.25<span>/KM</span></h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="box-img">
                            <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/1056x594/n/cw/ec/41197/hyundai-verna-right-front-three-quarter7.jpeg?q=75&wm=1"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Hyundai Verna</h3>
                        <h2>Rs.18<span>/KM</span></h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="box-img">
                            <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/1056x594/n/cw/ec/120405/kwid-exterior-right-front-three-quarter.jpeg?isig=0&q=75&wm=1"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Renault Kwid</h3>
                        <h2>Rs.17<span>/KM</span></h2>
                    </div>

                    <div class="box">
                        <div class="box-img">
                            <img src="https://imgd.aeplcdn.com/1056x594/n/cw/ec/47016/urban-cruiser-exterior-right-front-three-quarter-61.jpeg?isig=0&q=75&wm=1"
                                alt="">
                        </div>
                        <h3>Toyota Urban Cruiser</h3>
                        <h2>Rs.22<span>/KM</span></h2>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- About -->
            <section class="about" id="about">
                <div class="heading">
                    <span>About Us</span>
                    <h1>Best Customer Experience</h1>
                </div>

                <div class="about-container">
                    <div class="about-img">
                        <img src="https://github.com/ankul-agnihotri9627/pjuohk/blob/main/1194.jpg?raw=true" alt="car">
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-text">
                        <span>About Us</span>
                        <p>TOP is a community-based travel network enabling over 100 million members to share a
                            ride across 22 markets. Our leverages technology to fill empty seats on the road, connecting
                            members looking to carpool or to travel by bus, and making travel more affordable, sociable
                            and convenient. Our environmentally and human-friendly mobility network saves 1.6M tons of
                            CO2 and enables 120M human connections every year.</p>

                        <a href="/about-us" class="btn">Learn More</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Reviews -->

            <section class="reviews" id="reviews">
                <div class="heading">
                    <span>Reviews</span>
                    <h1>What Do Our Customer Say</h1>
                </div>

                <div class="bd-example">
                    <div id="carouselExampleCaptions" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
                            <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
                            <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="1"></li>
                            <li data-target="#carouselExampleCaptions" data-slide-to="2"></li>
                        </ol>
                        <div class="carousel-inner">
                            <div class="carousel-item active">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1534030347209-467a5b0ad3e6?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fm=jpg&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=80&raw_url=true&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=387"
                                    class="d-block" alt="...">
                                <div style="position: static;" class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                                    <h5>Kinshuk</h5>
                                    <p>I personally like this concept and services provided, if liked by me and my
                                        family I can book a car quickly and with in 5 min car comes to pick me up on my
                                        place and rate is also moderate.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1568602471122-7832951cc4c5?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fm=jpg&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=60&raw_url=true&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Mnx8bWFufGVufDB8fDB8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600" class="d-block" alt="...">
                                <div style="position: static;" class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                                    <h5>Harshit</h5>
                                    <p>I am a regular user. So I can assure so that it is better than cab operators. It
                                        is the cheapest mode of transportation in India. You have to pay as low as 15
                                        rupee per km for your ride if you choose a hatch-back (although price may differ
                                        from town to town and type of vehicle).</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="carousel-item">
                                <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539571696357-5a69c17a67c6?crop=entropy&cs=tinysrgb&fm=jpg&ixlib=rb-1.2.1&q=60&raw_url=true&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8OXx8bWFufGVufDB8fDB8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=600" class="d-block" alt="...">
                                <div style="position: static;" class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
                                    <h5>Ankul</h5>
                                    <p>The fairs are competitively low. The thing I loved most is that we get to
                                        interact with new people, and share the rides in most amazing ways. Still it can
                                        be improved. But still rocks!</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button"
                            data-slide="prev">
                            <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                        </a>
                        <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleCaptions" role="button"
                            data-slide="next">
                            <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                            <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <script src="https://unpkg.com/scrollreveal"></script>
</body>

<script src="main.js"></script>

</html>